Please send Guile YAMLPP bug reports to yorgath@gmail.com.

* Changes in 0.3 (since 0.2)

  - The ability to affect the format of emitted null values has been
    implemented.

  - Minimum yaml-cpp version is now 0.7.0.

* Changes in 0.2 (since 0.1)

  - All exported procedures are now documented.

  - New variables have been introduced which expose the manipulators
    that are valid for each type of YAML element:

    - yaml-string-manipulators
    - yaml-bool-manipulators
    - yaml-int-manipulators
    - yaml-seq-manipulators
    - yaml-map-manipulators
